Get calibration report for all agents.

Returns calibration metrics for all agents, sorted by status (worst first).

Includes summary statistics:
- Count by status (good/warning/poor/insufficient_data)
- Average ACE across calibrated agents

Note: include_bootstrap=False by default for performance. Set to True
for confidence intervals (adds ~1s per agent).
